<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-75-0504 </DOCNO><TEXT>To quantify the competitive position of natural gas in industrial fryingprocesses, market profiles were developed to define current technologiesand to characterize the applications and use of each technology in industrial-fryingapplications. Important cost and performance parameters were identifiedand validated through extensive interviews with industry representatives.Interviews also focused on current practices and fuel choice, expectationsfor future process developments that could affect natural gas use, andrecommendations for research that could improve the effectiveness ofgas-fired fryers.</TEXT></DOC>